<Grid
  xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
  xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
<Grid.RowDefinitions>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="10"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="10"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="10"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
    </Grid.RowDefinitions>
    <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="10"/>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
    </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
	<TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}">
	FLASH
	<LineBreak/>
	Z 150130Z JUN 85
	</TextBlock>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="FM"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="CTF 77"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="4" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="TO"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="4" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="COMMANDER {TaskForceName}"/>
	<TextBlock Grid.Row="5" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="INFO"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="5" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}">
		CINCPACFLT PEARL HARBOR HI<LineBreak/>
		HQ AIR COMMAND RAAF GLENBROOK NSW AU
	</TextBlock>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="7" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="SUBJ"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="7" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="RETASKING - MOVEMENT ORDERS TO DARWIN"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="9" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" TextWrapping="Wrap">
	  SECRET
	  <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
	  1. (S) SINGAPORE AND INDONESIA HAVE BEEN HEAVILY SUPPRESSED BY ENEMY ATTACKS 25JUN TO 14JUL AND THEIR STATUS IS UNCERTAIN. ALL U.S. FORCES IN SOUTHEAST ASIA ARE ORDERED TO NEW FALLBACK POSITION AT DARWIN, AUSTRALIA.
      <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
      2. (S) ALL UNITS {TaskForceName} PROCEED AT BEST SPEED TO DARWIN. EXIT JAVA SEA VIA SUNDA STRAIT.
      <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
	  3. (S) TANKER SEALIFT CARIBBEAN SEA WILL JOIN YOU AT JAKARTA.
	  <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
	  4. (S) ENEMY SURFACE FORCE REPORTED HEADING SOUTH AT FLANK SPEED, LIKELY INTENDING TO CLOSE SUNDA STRAIT TO ALLIED TRANSIT.
	  <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
	  5. (S) ENEMY ADVANCE FORCE AND SUBMARINES ARE LIKELY ACTIVE AROUND SUNDA STRAIT.
	  <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
	  6. (S) ONCE CLEAR OF THE STRAIT, ROYAL AUSTRALIAN AIR FORCE F-111 FLIGHTS WILL REPORT IN FOR SURFACE CAP AND ESCORT YOU TO DARWIN. GOOD LUCK.
	  <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
	  SECRET
	  <LineBreak/>
	  DECL OADR BT
	  </TextBlock>

</Grid>